properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 2 at 2:07PM CST until February 2 at 10:00PM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
* WHAT...West gusts up to 30 knots.

* WHERE...Sheboygan WI to Winthrop Harbor IL.

* WHEN...Until 10 PM CST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Strongest gusts will be this afternoon then
decrease this evening.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 PM CST THIS EVENING... ...GALE WARNING IS CANCELLED
